'''奧博莫紹'''（'''Ogbomosho'''）是[[尼日利亞|尼日利亞]]西南部[[奧約州|奧約州]]的城市，在十七世紀中期建立<ref name=eb>{{cite web|url= http://www.britannica.com/eb/article-9056821/Ogbomosho|title= Ogbomosho|accessdate= 2007-04-01|work= Britannica Online|publisher= Encyclopædia Britannica, Inc|archive-date= 2008-01-30|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20080130074851/http://www.britannica.com/eb/article-9056821/Ogbomosho|dead-url= no}}</ref>，1991年人口約645,000<ref name=columbia>{{cite encyclopedia | editor = Chernow, Barbara A; George A. Vallasi | encyclopedia = Columbia Encyclopedia | title = Ogbomosho | url = http://columbia.thefreedictionary.com/Ogbomosho | accessdate = 2007-04-01 | edition = 5th ed | year = 1993 | publisher = Columbia University Press | pages = 1997 | archive-date = 2006-02-10 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20060210224039/http://columbia.thefreedictionary.com/Ogbomosho | dead-url = yes }}</ref>，而2005年3月估計人口增加至約1,200,000<ref name=diocese>{{cite web|url= http://www.ogbomosodiocese.org/history.html|title= History|accessdate= 2007-04-01|work= ogbomosodiocese.org|publisher= Ogbomoso Missionary Diocese|deadurl= yes|archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20070929180122/http://www.ogbomosodiocese.org/history.html|archivedate= 2007-09-29}}</ref>。

奧博莫紹的居民主要是[[約魯巴人|約魯巴人]]，以種植[[木薯|木薯]]、[[玉米|玉米]]、[[煙草|煙草]]等農產品為生。<ref name=columbia/>

